This paper deals with optimization techniques for Markov Decision Processes (MDPs), which are commonly studied in the fields of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also involves linear programming and optimization (cs.DS), as well as control systems (cs.SY) and mathematical analysis (cs.MA).
